%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bch/Nam-x%C3%A1/poem-PNy4F-zFrSBZVotcbuXvMA">Nam xá - 南垞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bch/author-28bVUu4eMEqyWDansRayiw">Bùi Địch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Chi-V%E1%BA%A5n/S%C6%A1-t%C3%BAc-Ho%C3%A0i-Kh%E1%BA%A9u/poem-aegas_6ejagpNjpVWlI1-g">Sơ túc Hoài Khẩu - 初宿淮口</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Chi-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-ugO5moh7gzYYDOe2gVJzDg">Tống Chi Vấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-D%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BA%A1p-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-4TfB7KhYyldLQLeNIG5GAQ">Tạp vịnh kỳ 1 - 雜詠其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-D%E1%BB%B1c/author-63sQ6igz79c8AB4tN4pK2g">Quách Dực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%89nh-%C4%91%E1%BB%83-d%E1%BA%ABn-ng%C3%A2n-b%C3%ACnh/poem-fEvivJabPd3uwuqTNX3otg">Tỉnh để dẫn ngân bình - 井底引銀瓶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Bao-H%C3%A0/T%E1%BB%91ng-%C3%94-Tr%C3%ACnh-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-minh-ph%E1%BB%A7-bi%E1%BA%BFm-Ba-giang/poem-V6YIZpQqYRLE5vqngkbB6A">Tống Ô Trình Vương minh phủ biếm Ba giang - 送烏程王明府貶巴江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Bao-H%C3%A0/author-Al1aHrGQTzcKkvfhPwdKFA">Bao Hà</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
